Extraordinary CBT chrome extension is an extension specifically for use in exams in the Extraordinary CBT application. Extraordinary CBT is a computer-based exam application.

This Chrome extension functions to prevent exam participants from committing cheating actions such as opening another tab, opening another URL, leaving the tab, and close the chrome app.

It is hoped that this chrome extension will slightly reduce attempts at cheating.
